All containers have the same aspect ratio. The consistent warm-stone background simulates a consistent photography style. The grid reads unified.

## Quick Recap

- Bad images: unrelated stock photos, inconsistent styles, wrong aspect ratios.
- Good images: consistent color, appropriate subject, fixed aspect ratio containers.
- Use fixed aspect ratios so images never distort.
- Visual consistency across images matters as much as individual quality.
